1
00:00:00,729 --> 00:00:05,807
The first room was full, about 75 to 100 people

2
00:00:06,354 --> 00:00:08,724
And I came to this second room, it was full too

3
00:00:10,234 --> 00:00:12,500
I came through this door

4
00:00:13,411 --> 00:00:15,521
I entered from here, and I saw someone sitting here

5
00:00:16,823 --> 00:00:17,943
I was young then

6
00:00:17,968 --> 00:00:20,104
He said–What's your charge? I told him, Theft

7
00:00:21,302 --> 00:00:23,932
He said–People accused of theft don't sit with me here in the hall

8
00:00:24,375 --> 00:00:26,198
They go to the hall in front of me

9
00:00:26,953 --> 00:00:29,505
We started shouting at each other, then he went quiet

10
00:00:30,443 --> 00:00:32,578
I went in and sat here for a bit

11
00:00:32,603 --> 00:00:33,724
Interviewer: Why were you shouting at each other?

12
00:00:34,245 --> 00:00:38,151
He said to me–People who steal don't stay with me here in the hall

13
00:00:38,176 --> 00:00:39,635
They don't sit here with us

14
00:00:40,938 --> 00:00:43,073
So I sat here for a bit

15
00:00:44,849 --> 00:00:50,318
So I moved away from him and sat here, where five to six people were sleeping

16
00:00:50,812 --> 00:00:52,610
Wrapped in a blanket

17
00:00:53,131 --> 00:00:55,631
The same as this one, and they had put it here

18
00:00:56,672 --> 00:00:58,651
So I came here, laid my head down, and slept

19
00:00:59,980 --> 00:01:02,870
I woke up at night, they brought us food and we ate

20
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:05,995
Interviewer: Did you spend the first night in this room?
Witness: Yes

21
00:01:08,287 --> 00:01:10,292
Interviewer: When you woke up, did they bring you food after that?

22
00:01:10,448 --> 00:01:12,948
They brought the food and woke me up

23
00:01:12,973 --> 00:01:14,589
Interviewer: What kind of food did they give you on the first night?

24
00:01:15,110 --> 00:01:17,818
It was rice and soup

25
00:01:20,761 --> 00:01:22,792
Interviewer: And on the second day in the morning, what happened?

26
00:01:27,532 --> 00:01:31,672
The guards came in carrying the Lakhdar Brahimi hose

27
00:01:33,446 --> 00:01:36,076
Two came in here

28
00:01:36,101 --> 00:01:38,082
And three were standing here

29
00:01:38,107 --> 00:01:39,722
They were ISIS members

30
00:01:39,747 --> 00:01:41,571
And they were here in the first hall

31
00:01:42,535 --> 00:01:46,155
And there was a person standing here by the iron bars, watching

32
00:01:47,483 --> 00:01:49,853
To see who had banged on the bars

33
00:01:51,780 --> 00:01:54,410
Everyone said it wasn't them

34
00:01:55,191 --> 00:01:57,353
So they beat three or four of us and left

35
00:02:00,269 --> 00:02:02,118
Interviewer: Was this on the second day?

36
00:02:02,352 --> 00:02:06,441
And after that they issued a general amnesty

37
00:02:06,466 --> 00:02:07,951
Interviewer: After how many days?

38
00:02:08,352 --> 00:02:12,258
After about a month
